        "headerTitle": "Comparing Payment Methods",
        "layout": "generic",
        "layoutData": {
          "paragraphs": [
            "<strong>Best for:</strong> Large payments, rent, situations requiring documentation<br><br><strong>Processing time:</strong> 1-5 business days to clear<br><br><strong>Security:</strong> Can be stopped if lost; creates paper trail",
            "<strong>Best for:</strong> Everyday purchases, in-store and online shopping<br><br><strong>Processing time:</strong> Instant deduction from account<br><br><strong>Security:</strong> PIN protection; report lost cards immediately",
            "<strong>Best for:</strong> Cash withdrawals, quick balance checks, deposits<br><br><strong>Processing time:</strong> Instant for withdrawals<br><br><strong>Security:</strong> Use in-network ATMs; protect your PIN",
            "<strong>Best for:</strong> Bill payments, transfers, account monitoring<br><br><strong>Processing time:</strong> Same-day to 1-3 days for transfers<br><br><strong>Security:</strong> Use secure networks; enable 2-factor authentication"
