        "headerTitle": "Strategies to Avoid Fees",
        "layout": "concept-full",
        "layoutData": {
          "title": "Smart Banking Means Fewer Fees",
          "paragraphs": [
            "With a few simple habits, you can eliminate most banking fees and keep more of your hard-earned money:",
            "Check your account regularly through online banking or the mobile app. Set up low balance alerts to warn you before you overspend.",
            "Find your bank's ATM locator on their app. Plan ahead to avoid using out-of-network machines that charge extra fees.",
            "Maintain minimum balances or set up direct deposit. Many banks waive monthly fees with qualifying activities. Consider credit unions like {{STATE_LOCAL_CREDIT_UNION_NAME}} in {{STATE_NAME}} which often offer lower fees."
          ],
